description:
I got the chance to try Frozen Kuhsterd at a recent Yelp event. The available flavors were horchata latte and cereal milk. Of course, I asked for one of each.. (; 

The horchata latte was basically a coffee flavor. I love the taste of coffee, so I really enjoyed it. However, the cereal milk flavor blew my mind! It really tasted like cereal milk -- creamy with a hint of cinnamon. This is a flavor I would love to buy a gallon of to keep in my freezer. I can't recommend this particular flavor enough. 

The two employees serving us were both very nice and polite as well. I love it when small businesses have both a great product and great employees. I will definitely be on the lookout for this truck whenever I'm in town!
